## 🛠️ 3. SDK Payload Mapping

The SDK's `generate_script` and `compose_scene` stages consume this graph via structured injection.

| Story Graph Field | SDK Target | Mapping Logic |
|-------------------|------------|---------------|
| `narrative_arc.pacing_beats` | `parameters.pacing_map` | Drives syllable-to-seconds allocation in TTS & prosody engine. |
| `nodes[].accuracy` | `parameters.accuracy_mode` | Forces `[Verified]` nodes to literal phrasing; `[Speculative]` gets hedging language (`"Lore suggests..."`). |
| `scene_directives.broll_markers` | `compose_scene.parameters.broll_injections` | Auto-fetches archival/media assets at exact timestamps. |
| `scene_directives.gesture_cues` | `compose_scene.parameters.ik_triggers` | Maps to upper-body IK presets synced to audio peaks. |
| `metadata.primary_sources` | `parameters.source_data` | Embedded in C2PA manifest for provenance tracking. |

**SDK Payload Construction Example:**
```python
sdk_payload = {
  "meta": {"execution_mode": "async", "priority": "high"},
  "operation": "generate_script",
  "parameters": {
    "@op": "generate_script",
    "length_seconds": graph["narrative_arc"]["total_duration_sec"] or 180,
    "tone_profile": graph["pacing_beats"][0]["tone"],
    "story_graph_weights": {
      "causality_priority": 0.85,
      "emotional_arc_weight": 0.7,
      "historical_precision": 0.9
    },
    "override_prompt": f"STRUCTURE: {json.dumps(graph['narrative_arc']['act_1_setup'])} → TURN: {graph['narrative_arc']['act_2_turning_point']}",
    "compliance_tag": "auto_hedge_speculative"
  }
}
```

