## ⚙️ 5. Updated CI/CD Workflow

Add a **Graph Generation & Validation** step before SDK dispatch.

```yaml
# .github/workflows/aethel-render.yml (excerpt)
jobs:
  render:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-python@v5
        with: { python-version: "3.11" }
      - run: pip install aethel-sdk pydantic httpx

      # 🆕 STEP 1: Run/Load Story Graph
      - name: 🧠 Generate & Validate Story Graph
        run: python ci/story_graph_bridge.py
        env:
          STORY_GRAPH_API_URL: ${{ vars.STORY_GRAPH_ENDPOINT || 'http://localhost:8080/graph' }}

      # ✅ STEP 2: SDK Dispatch (reads config/render-payload.json)
      - name: 🚀 SDK Dispatch
        id: dispatch
        run: python ci/aethel_runner.py dispatch

      # ⏳ STEP 3: Poll & Download (unchanged)
      - name: ⏳ Monitor & Download
        if: success() && steps.dispatch.outputs.job_id
        run: |
          python ci/aethel_runner.py poll
          python ci/aethel_runner.py download

      - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: aethel-render-${{ github.run_id }}
          path: ./aethel_output/
```

