## ✅ 7. Validation & Fallback Rules

| Scenario | SDK/Graph Response |
|----------|-------------------|
| **Sparse Graph (<3 nodes)** | Falls back to `chronological` structure. Warns via CI log: `⚠️ Low node density. Using default 3-act template.` |
| **Conflicting Timestamps** | NLP resolver sorts by `confidence_score`. SDK injects `temporal_ambiguity_markers` for narrator hedging. |
| **Missing B-Roll Assets** | Auto-generates HDRI environment match via `style_profile`. Logs `broll_fallback: true` in C2PA metadata. |
| **Accuracy Mode Conflict** | If `accuracy_mode: verified_only` but graph contains `[Speculative]` nodes, CI fails with: `❌ Policy violation: Unverified nodes in strict mode.` |

